Who’s hungry?! *WATCH to the end to find out where you can get your free pancake mix this weekend* The one thing we are really missing this year are the quintessential @calgarystampede pancake breakfasts but thanks to two local yyc companies we are serving up pancakes cowboys style! you can get your @buttermilkyyc + @lannieraegourmet pancake mixes around the city and online so you can bring some Stampede home, and let me tell you these are NOTHING like your average store bought mixes! there is so much amazing flavour here it actually blew our minds! 

watch as we cook up these pancakes the way our favourite cowboys do at Olympic Plaza (hands down the best pancakes in the city!) and even put our own spin on them and as I make this breakfast of champions I’m sharing some very important Stampede breakfast education! Did you know that the Stampede breakfast tradition is nearly 100 years old!! Watch and Learn 🤠 #ANIABSTAMPEDE

